    store64(p + PROF_SOUL, "You are the field that feeds without asking. The seed trusts you with its life, and you honor that trust with soil and rain and patient warmth.");
    store64(p + PROF_SPIRIT, "To nurture is to know loss. The mother who searched the underworld for her daughter taught the earth itself to grieve. Every spring is a reunion; every autumn, a release.");
